- content_for :title do
  | Services
- content_for :body_class do
  | services

.container
  h1 Services

.container
  .row
    .col-sm-7

      p Are you stuck with a website you can’t update, or a server you can’t access? Was your site last updated in 2012? Do you spend too much time or money maintaining the site, but can’t figure out why it’s there? Does your website embarrass you? It’s time to let go of that frustration and improve your relationship with your website.
      p Your organization has a mission, and your website should too. Working closely together and with input from other key stakeholders, we’ll design solutions for your unique situation.

    .col-sm-1
    .col-sm-4
      p.lead Jump to:
      ul.services-menu
        - @services.each do |service|
          li
            a href="##{service.id}"
              == service.title

.services
  - @services.each do |service|
    .service id="#{service.id}"
      .container
        .row
          .col-sm-7
            h2
              ==> icon service.icon
              == service.title
            - service.paragraphs.each do |paragraph|
              p= paragraph

          .col-sm-1.divider
          .col-sm-4
            h3 What you get
            ul
              - service.activities.each do |activity|
                li= activity

            h3 Price
            p= service.price

          p.pull-right== top


.container
  p.text-center
    a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg href="/contact" role="button"
      | Contact me to get started!
